            </div>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"navi__list--item has-child\" data-page=\"jobs\">\n                <div class=\"list-wrap js-has-child\" data-label=\"jobs\">\n                  <p>ニチコンの仕事</p><span class=\"arrow-ico\" data-label=\"jobs\"></span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"child-list__wrap\" data-label=\"jobs\">\n                  <ul class=\"child-list\">\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/\">\n                        <p>ニチコンの仕事TOP</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/interview1.html\">\n                        <p>フィルムコンデンサ設計</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/interview2.html\">\n                        <p>生産技術</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/interview3.html\">\n                        <p>材料開発</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/interview4.html\">\n                        <p>品質管理</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/interview5.html\">\n                        <p>社内SE</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/interview6.html\">\n                        <p>コンデンサ設計開発</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/interview7.html\">\n                        <p>蓄電ソフト開発</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/interview8.html\">\n                        <p>応用機器設計</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/jobs/interview10.html\">\n                        <p>営業</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"navi__list--item\" data-page=\"technology\"><a href=\"/recruit_graduates/technology/\">\n                  <div class=\"list-wrap\">\n                    <p>未来をひらく技術力</p><span class=\"c-arrow-only-ico is-tab\"></span>\n                  </div></a></li>\n              <li class=\"navi__list--item\" data-page=\"internship\"><a href=\"/recruit_graduates/internship/\">\n                  <div class=\"list-wrap\">\n                    <p>インターンシップ</p><span class=\"c-arrow-only-ico is-tab\"></span>\n                  </div></a></li>\n              <li class=\"navi__list--item last-item has-child\" data-page=\"requirement\">\n                <div class=\"list-wrap js-has-child\" data-label=\"requirement\">\n                  <p>募集要項</p><span class=\"arrow-ico\" data-label=\"requirement\"></span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"child-list__wrap is-open\" data-label=\"requirement\">\n                  <ul class=\"child-list\">\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/requirement/\">\n                        <p>募集要項TOP</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"child-list__item\"><a class=\"flex-box\" href=\"/recruit_graduates/requirement/process.html\">\n                        <p>採用プロセス</p>\n                        <div class=\"c-arrow-only-ico\"></div></a></li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"header__entry--wrap\"><a class=\"header__entry--btn -white\" href=\"https://job.axol.jp/bx/s/nichicon_27/mypage/login\" target=\"_blank\">\n              <p>My Page</p></a><a class=\"header__entry--btn\" href=\"https://job.axol.jp/bx/s/nichicon_27/entry/\" target=\"_blank\">\n              <p>Entry</p></a></div>\n          <div class=\"sp-menu__btn\" id=\"js-menu-btn\">\n            <p>Menu</p><span class=\"border-ico\"></span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n    <div class=\"process\">\n      <section class=\"process-mv\">\n        <div class=\"process-mv__container\">\n          <div class=\"process-mv__img\">\n            <div class=\"c-container\">\n              <div class=\"c-ttl__contents\">\n                <h2 class=\"c-ttl white-txt u-textOverlay\"><span class=\"u-textOverlay__inner\">Process</span></h2>\n                <p class=\"c-sub-ttl white-txt u-textOverlay\"><span class=\"u-textOverlay__inner\">採用プロセス</span></p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n      <div class=\"process-anchor__container\">\n        <div class=\"c-anchor-links\">\n          <div class=\"c-anchor-link\"><a class=\"c-btn\" href=\"#recommend\">\n              <div class=\"c-btn__txt\">推薦応募</div></a></div>\n          <div class=\"c-anchor-link\"><a class=\"c-btn\" href=\"#free\">\n              <div class=\"c-btn__txt\">自由応募</div></a></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <section class=\"process-recommend\" id=\"recommend\">\n        <div class=\"process-contents__container\">\n          <div class=\"c-container\">\n            <h2 class=\"c-lower-ttl\">推薦応募<span class=\"c-blue-label\">理工系</span></h2>\n            <div class=\"process-contents__wrap\">\n              <div class=\"process-contents__inner\">\n                <div class=\"process-contents__lead\">\n                  <p>応募書類一式を当社人事部宛に<br class=\"is-sp\">お送りください。<br class=\"is-only-tab\">別途採用選考（面接等）の日時を<br class=\"is-sp\">ご連絡します。</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"process-recommend__column\">\n                  <div class=\"process-recommend__column--item\">\n                    <div class=\"ttl\">応募書類</div>\n                    <div class=\"txt\">エントリーフォーム、履歴書、成績証明書、<br class=\"is-sp\">卒業（修了）見込証明書、<br class=\"is-sp\">推薦書</div>\n                    <div class=\"comment-box\"><small class=\"comment\">※大学院を修了予定の方は、学部時の成績証明書、卒業証明書も併せて提出ください。</small><small class=\"comment\">※応募時点で提出可能な書類をお送りください。</small></div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"process-recommend__column--item\">\n                    <div class=\"ttl\">送付先</div>\n                    <div class=\"txt\">〒604-0845　<br class=\"is-tab\">京都市中京区烏丸通御池上る<br>ニチコン株式会社　管理本部人事部</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n      <section class=\"process-free js-fadeup-trigger\" id=\"free\">\n        <div class=\"process-contents__container\">\n          <div class=\"c-container\">\n            <h2 class=\"c-lower-ttl\">自由応募<span class=\"c-blue-label\">理工系</span><span class=\"c-red-label\">文系</span></h2>\n            <div class=\"process-contents__wrap\">\n              <div class=\"process-contents__inner\">\n                <div class=\"process-flow\">\n                  <div class=\"process-flow__wrap\">\n                    <div class=\"process-flow__item\">\n                      <div class=\"flow-step\">Step</div>\n                      <div class=\"flow-ttl\">エントリー</div>\n                      <div class=\"flow-img\"><img src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/images/process/process-flow-img01.svg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"process-flow__item\">\n                      <div class=\"flow-step\">Step</div>\n                      <div class=\"flow-ttl\">会社説明会</div>\n                      <div class=\"flow-img\"><img src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/images/process/process-flow-img02.svg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"process-flow__item\">\n                      <div class=\"flow-step\">Step</div>\n                      <div class=\"flow-ttl\">応募書類<br class=\"is-sp\">提出</div>\n                      <div class=\"flow-img\"><img src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/images/process/process-flow-img03.svg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"process-flow__item\">\n                      <div class=\"flow-step\">Step</div>\n                      <div class=\"flow-ttl\">選考</div>\n                      <div class=\"flow-img\"><img src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/images/process/process-flow-img04.svg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"process-free__step\">\n                  <div class=\"process-free__step--inner\">\n                    <div class=\"step__list\">\n                      <dl class=\"step__list--item\">\n                        <dt class=\"step\">Step</dt>\n                        <dd class=\"txt-box\">\n                          <p class=\"ttl\">エントリー</p>\n                          <p class=\"txt\">当社の選考に参加いただくにあたり、まずは採用HPより<br class=\"is-tab\">エントリーしてください。</p>\n                        </dd>\n                      </dl>\n                      <dl class=\"step__list--item\">\n                        <dt class=\"step\">Step</dt>\n                        <dd class=\"txt-box\">\n                          <p class=\"ttl\">会社説明会</p>\n                          <p class=\"txt\">マイページからお申し込みできます。<br>【録画配信型】と【ライブ配信型】のどちらかを選択し、<br class=\"is-tab\">ご参加ください。</p>\n                        </dd>\n                      </dl>\n                      <dl class=\"step__list--item\">\n                        <dt class=\"step\">Step</dt>\n                        <dd class=\"txt-box\">\n                          <p class=\"ttl\">応募書類 提出</p>\n                          <p class=\"txt\">応募書類：エントリーフォーム、履歴書、成績証明書、卒業（修了）見込証明書、<br class=\"is-tab\">推薦書</p><small class=\"comment\">※大学院を修了予定の方は、学部時の成績証明書、卒業証明書も併せて提出ください。</small><small class=\"comment\">※応募時点で提出可能な書類をお送りください。</small>\n                          <div class=\"address\">\n                            <div class=\"address-ttl\">送付先</div>\n                            <div class=\"address-txt\">〒604-0845　<br class=\"is-sp\">京都市中京区烏丸通御池上る<br>ニチコン株式会社　<br class=\"is-sp\">管理本部人事部</div>\n                          </div>\n                        </dd>\n                      </dl>\n                      <dl class=\"step__list--item\">\n                        <dt class=\"step\">Step</dt>\n                        <dd class=\"txt-box\">\n                          <p class=\"ttl\">選考</p>\n                          <p class=\"txt\">作文<br>面接(2~3回)</p>\n                        </dd>\n                      </dl>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </div>\n    <footer class=\"l-footer\">\n      <div class=\"footer__container\">\n        <div class=\"footer__inner\">\n          <div class=\"footer__link\">\n            <div class=\"footer__link--item\"><a href=\"https://www.nichicon.co.jp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n                <p>コーポレートサイト</p></a></div>\n            <div class=\"footer__link--item\"><a href=\"https://www.nichicon.co.jp/policy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n                <p>個人情報保護方針</p></a></div>\n          </div><small class=\"footer__copy\">© 2024  NICHICON CORPORATION.</small>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </footer>\n    <script src=\"/recruit_graduates/assets/js/app.js\"></script>\n  </body>\n</html>","finalUrl":"http://www.nichicon.co.jp/recruit_graduates/requirement/process.html","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T17:32:14.415Z"}